notes.name: 5-minute body scan
notes.text: The body-scan meditation is a soothing practice that cultivates calmness and presence by systematically focusing on and relaxing each part of the body, promoting deep relaxation and a heightened sense of body awareness.

notes.name: Progressive Muscle Relaxation
notes.text: Progressive Muscle Relaxation (PMR) is a guided exercise that involves systematically tensing and releasing different muscle groups in the body, promoting deep relaxation, stress reduction, and body-mind connection.
